# Generated artifacts that should NOT be committed (drafts before review)
reports/daily/*.draft.md
reports/monthly/*.draft.md
reports/buy_shortlist/*.draft.md
# raw_signal_pack 中間產物，不入長期版控（見 scripts/README）。
# 注意：workflow/prompt 實際產出的副檔名是 *.signals.yml（不是 *.raw_signals.yml）——
# 兩者統一為 *.signals.yml，避免命名漂移讓 gitignore 對真實中間產物失效（2026-06-16）。
reports/daily/*.signals.yml
